Acme::rot13

This packages implements the high security Rot13 encryption algorithm. More info see: https://secure.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/wiki/Rot13

USAGE

To use this module in your code, you need to first load the module using:

use Acme::rot13;

Then simply use the function encrypt() passing a string, eg.:

encrypt("a string of text to encrypt");

See also /t/rot13Test.t




